{"title":"Vue Update Background Style Inside a Component","slug":"vue-update-background-style-inside-component","tags":["vue"],"created_at":"2021-06-24T01:28:33.864Z","content":"<p>First, create a element in template:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;div v-html=&quot;&#39;&lt;style&gt;&#39;+styleText+&#39;&lt;/style&gt;&#39;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Then change the value of <code>styleText</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">styleText: `\nbody {\n  background: #ffe4c4;\n}\n`.trim()\n</code></pre>\n<p>The style will update if the value of <code>styleText</code> changed. The style will also be removed after the component unmounted.</p>\n","category_id":"1","category":{"name":"Front-end","id":"1","slug":"frontend","alternate":{"en":"frontend","zh":"frontend"}},"alternate":{"en":"vue-update-background-style-inside-component","zh":"vue-update-background-style-inside-component"}}